- "total amount spent" is the sum of all payments made by the customer for their orders;
- "preferred measurement unit" is the unit of measurement (e.g., cm, inches) that the customer prefers;
- "preferred category ID" is the ID of the clothing category that the customer prefers.

- 'Most recent' refers to the latest preference based on the last order date;
